data.description: BETTER THAN NEW!! This Gorgeous home is Like New and offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with a bonus room and a beautiful view of the community lake. The entry welcomes you with hardwood floors and a view of the formal dining room and great room. The great room has hardwood floors, gas log fireplace and a nice open view into the kitchen. The kitchen has hardwood floors along with a breakfast/snack bar, under-cabinet lighting, beautiful granite counter tops, custom cabinets and a cozy breakfast area. The master bedroom has a HUGE salon bath with walk-thru shower, soaker tub, double vanities and a large walk in closet.
